While some of us are counting down the days until pay day, the Idols SA judge has spoilt himself with a brand new BMW i8, which according to the manufacturer's website is worth over R1.7 million.And of course, his old lady had to bless the car, before making its way onto the streets.An excited Somizi took to Instagram to share a snap of his mother inside his newly-purchased beast."Went to see my living ancestor. For 10 min. I'm recharged for the entire week. Seeing her eyes beaming with pride makes me wanna work harder and fly higher. Thank u Ma," he wrote alongside the adorable picture.A photo posted by Somizi (@somizi) on Oct 16, 2016 at 5:37am PDT Since then, the car has been blessed by Somizi's equally-famous close friends, including Khanyi Mbau and Maps Maponyane.A photo posted by Somizi (@somizi) on Oct 18, 2016 at 5:33am PDT A video posted by Khanyi Mbau METANOIA (@mbaureloaded) on Oct 18, 2016 at 11:43pm PDT Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter.